{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sourceSetNameByID"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"tag"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"name"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CChar","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5CChara"},{"kind":"text","text":">!)"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a convenience utility to set source names from the return"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.idle_add"},{"type":"text","text":"], [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.timeout_add"},{"type":"text","text":"], etc."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is a programmer error to attempt to set the name of a non-existent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"More specifically: source IDs can be reissued after a source has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"destroyed and therefore it is never valid to use this function with a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source ID which may have already been removed.  An example is when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"scheduling an idle to run in another thread with [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.idle_add"},{"type":"text","text":"]: the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"idle may already have run and been removed by the time this function"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is called on its (now invalid) source ID.  This source ID may have"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"been reissued, leading to the operation being performed against the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"wrong source."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/sourcesetnamebyid(tag:name:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/sourceSetNameByID(tag:name:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the name of a source using its ID."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sourceSetNameByID"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"tag"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"name"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CChar","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5CChara"},{"kind":"text","text":">!)"}],"title":"sourceSetNameByID(tag:name:)","roleHeading":"Function","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"func","externalID":"s:4GLib17sourceSetNameByID3tag4nameySi_SPys4Int8VGSgtF","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/sourceSetNameByID(tag:name:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"sourceSetNameByID(tag:name:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sourceSetNameByID"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"tag"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"te